{"data":[{"id":560439220,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9ae5ccfe3b05ca3bddbca4501b5cb76b","url_token":"xiao-yidao-9825","name":"萧一刀","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8a16363bf7b7e5f4c67a86b117f5c74b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8a16363bf7b7e5f4c67a86b117f5c74b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9ae5ccfe3b05ca3bddbca4501b5cb76b","user_type":"people","headline":"克莱登大学法学博士","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":91,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560439220","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545837792,"updated_time":1545838791,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":122,"comment_count":13,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e同为高中生（当然，作为一个文科生中的弱鸡，我数学肯定没有题主好），说一下对本事件的看法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先请容许我称赞该同学的大胆想法，科学的路上一定需要敢闯敢拼的精神，否则大家都在难题面前畏畏缩缩，人类的科技发展便无从谈起。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但我同样也反对题主的大跃进式的蛮干。原因如下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e论文实在不适合发表在知乎这样的平台，缺少编辑的专业把关不说，还容易招来网络暴力。\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥猜令世界上无数的数学家为之沉迷，但他们最终还是功败垂成，可见哥猜难度的确不是一般的大。当然世界级难题不乏被黑马解决的事例，可这终究是极个别的例子。如前面有答主贴出的陈景润的著作导言所述，青年人不要在哥猜上浪费宝贵的时间。\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e网络上充满了所谓“哥猜证明”，甚至一些审稿不严谨的学术刊物上也刊载有相关文章。但至今学术界权威并没有理睬这些民科人士。\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003e综上，还请这位同学\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e咨询专业人士（最好是比你的数学老师和奥赛教练更厉害的数学研究者），让他们给出能让你心服口服的意见。\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e全面客观认识自己，争取好好学习，依靠现有可行性高的制度（高考、自主招生等）考入名校。\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003e也请广大吃瓜群众\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e拒绝网络暴力\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e认真对待，替题主解开心结，别让身怀数学一技之长的他沦为落入民科逻辑陷阱一辈子走不出来的废柴\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真心祝愿这位同学能够充分发挥自己的优势，补足短板，考入理想的大学。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"同为高中生（当然，作为一个文科生中的弱鸡，我数学肯定没有题主好），说一下对本事件的看法。首先请容许我称赞该同学的大胆想法，科学的路上一定需要敢闯敢拼的精神，否则大家都在难题面前畏畏缩缩，人类的科技发展便无从谈起。但我同样也反对题主的大跃进…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=72\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan